data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath, brick ranch home in established ParkView neighborhood. This home has been updated with a modern eat-in kitchen, lots of cabinets, and a breakfast bar. Some features include hardwood floors, ceramic tile, updated bathrooms, and a big backyard. The primary ensuite includes a spacious walk-in closet. The fenced backyard is perfect for pets and entertaining, with plenty of room for finishing the large deck, and adding a pool, fire pit, or an additional storage shed. This home is located close to downtown Portsmouth, Naval Medical Center, and the Elizabeth River. You’ll enjoy the convenience of shopping, restaurants, and other amenities. Schedule a showing today!
